\"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's everything you need to know about the 2024 ParisOlympics, including key dates and how to watch.\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympicevents began on Wednesday, July 24, 2024 with football,rugby, handball, and archery tournaments before the opening ceremony on Friday, July 26.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games will end on Sunday, August 11.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris will then host the Paralympic Games from Wednesday, August 28 to Sunday, September 8.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.973969589241968e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The following sports are included in this year's Olympic Games:  Tickets areon salenow, and thecost can differ significantlyfrom between roughly \\u20ac24 (\\u00a321) and \\u20ac2,400 (\\u00a32,100).\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most websites say they are mostly already sold out for swimming and beach volleyball events.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information on Paris 2024, visit the official websitehere.\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.337632064082912e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TV channel:The BBC has announced it will broadcast two live streams of the action from July 27 to August 11 - for the duration of the Games.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999999913598, \"rank\": 8.577970017846369e-12, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be on BBC One, BBC Two or a stream available by clicking the red button on Freeview or a smart TV.\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freeview_(UK)\", \"score\": 0.9827493944847808, \"rank\": 0.01580453340061992, \"text\": \"Freeview\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freeview_(UK)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freeview_(UK)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is reduced coverage compared with previous years, however, when BBC broadcasted everything from archery to wrestling live on its website or channels.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999999913598, \"rank\": 8.577970017846369e-12, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Discovery+ is the rights holder for Paris 2024 and is showing every moment across Eurosport channels in the UK from 7am-10.30pm every day.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.337632064082912e-19, \"text\"